This is a collection of addon pieces for my Shipping Containers (https://www.thingiverse.com/thing:6753917) to turn them into varios Shops or if you want to, into makeshift homes for your Hive citizens or Ash waste citizens.
Of course you can use the pieces on any other building. These pieces are designed to fit the container sides though and I plan to upload modified pieces in a seperate pack later.

Overview.PDF in the files for easier navigation

I recommend my "Bits for Scifi Buildings" Packs for further decorating the pieces.


I think it should be mostly self explanatory, if not feel free to ask.

Some fittings to connect drinking straws to make pipes for your wargaming terrain.

The connection point is made for a inner straw diameter of 8,6mm.
To find out in what size you need to print it for your drinking straws use the following formula:

("Your diameter" x 100) / 8,6 = print at ... %

I added an excel file where you can get your print scale easy.

Some connector bitz to use drinking straws as pipes in your scratchbuild wargaming terrain.

For a long time now I avoided using drinking straws in my wargaming scenery builds because i simply didn't like the bending part. It always squished and looked arkward.
Today i came up with this rather simple but effective solution. 3D printed connectors!

The drinking straws I had had a inner diameter of 6.6mm.

If your drinking straws have a different diameter just calculate the needed scaling using the excel sheet i added or by hand [("your diameter" x 100) / 6,6]

There is a version of each connector with and without the part that goes into the drinking straw to secure it.
